firefly-logger (26.0-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  *  Dark mode! Toggle light and dark mode from the menu in the top-right
  *  Shaded map to track QSO progress!
  *  Updated form validation system using jQuery Validate Library
  *  Fully-responsive design; removed legacy layout that did not work well on
     smaller screens
  *  An "All QSOs" screen with filtering and searching features
  *  Added a ping/polling feature to the main log screen and the board display to
     bring up an unmissable and unclearable alert if the connection to the server
     drops
  *  All Ajax/XHR calls now properly validate and report on errors
  *  Editing a QSO did not change the qkey index value leading to potential
     collisions
  *  Operator field was not always properly uppercasing
  *  Cleanup old JavaScript code
  *  Replacement of inline SVG with Bootstrap Icons
  *  Upgrade of jQuery
  *  Upgrade of Bootstrap
  *  Replacement of the Twitter typeahead library with a minimalist custom
     solution
  *  Much more robust error handling
  *  Transition to MySQL PDO for database 

 -- Helium <jason@mfamily.org>  Sun, 10 May 2026 20:36:53 -0400

